               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image 1r: Asmat prayer against charm, ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡., appealing to the five wounds of Jesus. Images 2-3l: Asmat prayers. Images 3r-64l: Gospel of John, ወንጌል፡ ዘዮሐንስ፡, arranged for the days of the week, with explanations of the text in the bottom margins, incomplete at the end (through chapter 19). M. G. Wechsler, Evangelium Iohannis Aethiopicum, CSCO 617, SA 109 (2005). Illuminations are added recently, over the top of text. Image 64r, col. 1: Asmat prayer. Image 64r, col 2: Geneology of a family in ተጉለት and መንዝቃጥ regions in the Amhara region. Image 65l: illegible.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
